OL,5,G2210 The Madame Blanc Mysteries
OL,6,     FPatrick tells Jean that 30 years
OL,7,     Fago he was responsible for
OL,8,     Fidentifying Sonny, a man sentenced
OL,9,     Fto 30 years in prison. Can Jean
OL,10,     Fsolve a mystery before Sonny
OL,11,     Freturns to take revenge?
